com.android.carousel

Class CarouselActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • com.android.carousel.CarouselActivity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DialogButtonClickListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OptionsControllerActivity, SystemControllerActivity, SystemControllerHelpActivity

    public class CarouselActivity
extends Activity
implements DialogButtonClickListener
    Represents a layout based on a "carousel". Menu item are moved by gestures to the left and right. T he base class for all such views in the application.

    tomasz
